{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"致古巴","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":24}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致古巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲怒吼了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海沸腾了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马埃斯特腊山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响起一阵阵春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里雷声万里闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶的锁链已被粉碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的旗子升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀也参加作战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在这里听见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的光荣的宣言——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫革命政权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前决不后退。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷响吧更响些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前决不退让；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗子已经升起了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也不会下降；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿尔贝蒂说得好："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“杀人者自取灭亡！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上已出现朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风为你们歌唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由、民主、独立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是人民的生命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘蔗林子棕榈树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是英雄的篷帐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷响吧更响些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要为你发言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢来点起战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们做你的后盾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把昆仑山高高举起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作人民的铁拳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘蔗本是甜蜜树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何有了苦味？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道不是美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒下毒药和苦水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴要把甘蔗田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成一座幸福园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪廉说甘蔗田里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一支永恒发射的箭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们捧起海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为这支利箭举杯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为一切革命战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献上花朵和诗篇！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}